<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>SilverTongued | The Altar of Greatness</title>
        <style>
            body {
                background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Sleek, powerful dark mode */
                color: #f4f4f4;
                font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 100px 20px;
                background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('your-background.jpg');
                background-size: cover;
            }
            .profile-photo {
                width: 250px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                border: 4px solid #d4af37; /* Gold "Empress" border */
                transform: scaleX(-1); /* THE FLIP: Makes you look toward the text */
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
            }
            .mantra {
                font-style: italic;
                font-size: 1.5em;
                color: #d4af37;
                margin: 20px auto;
                max-width: 600px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 50px;
                line-height: 1.8;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="header">
            <img src="your-photo.jpg" class="profile-photo" alt="The Empress">
            
            <h1>SilverTongued</h1>
            <p class="mantra">"Embody Greatness within the Altar of yourself, and the Universe has no choice but to reflect that Greatness back to the world through you."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>The Cave is Closed.</h2>
            <p>You aren't here by accident. You are here because the 'Trouble' has been disposed of, and it is time to build your Empire on Logic, Intuition, and Sovereignty.</p>
        </div>

    </body>
</html>
